Charming Two Bedroom Apartment in Columbia Heights Available Early July!<br>
<br>
<br>
The main living area features beautiful hardwood floors, exposed brick walls, and lots of natural light. The kitchen features a large breakfast island, gas range, and dishwasher!  Throughout the rest of the apartment, you will notice the lovely tile work in the bathroom and several spacious closets!<br>
<br>
Located only four blocks from the Columbia Heights Metro, this apartment is anchored by many options for groceries, dining, and nightlife.  In addition to the Columbia Heights Metro, several bus lines run along Sherman and Georgia Avenues as well as along other nearby streets.<br>
<br>
Move-in ready by early July.  Tenants are responsible for electric and internet/cable (if desired).  Water, gas, and trash are included in the rental price.  Laundry room on site.  The rental application is $50 per adult.  The minimum credit score for consideration is 670 (per DC statute, the approval decision is not based solely on the credit score).  A minimum one (1) year lease is required.<br>
<br>
This rental unit is professionally managed by Scout Properties, DC's trustworthy property management firm, located in the Brookland neighborhood of Washington, DC.  Scout Properties follows Equal Opportunity Housing guidelines, and Federal/DC Laws, which includes voucher assistance and "source of income" protected classes. Contact Ben Sanders for a showing today!!<br>
